===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|vermelioun}}, {{m|enm|vermyloun}}, {{m|enm|vermylon}}, {{m|enm|vermilun}}, {{der|en|fro|vermeillon|t=vermilion}}, from {{m|fro|vermeil}}, from {{der|en|la|vermiculus|t=little worm}}, from {{m|la|vermis|t=worm}}, ultimately in reference to {{taxlink|Kermes vermilio|species|noshow=1}}, a type of scale insect used to make a crimson dye.

